  "Allegations" : "ON OR ABOUT APRIL 16, 1993 JASON MACKENIZE SECURITIES, INC. (\"JMC\") FILED DOCUMENTS WITH THE DIVISION TO BECOME REGISTERED AS A BROKER- DEALER IN MASSACHUSETTS.
